All Classes

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddPartController
    Handles all events within the AddPart window.
    AddProductController
    Handles all events within the AddProduct window.
    Controller
    Responsible for handling all buttons as well as table display & functionality on the main page.
    InHouse
    Subclass of part which is produced in-house.
    Inventory
    Contains ObservableLists containing all Parts & Products, as well as methods to add, lookup, update, and delete items from those lists.
    Main
    The Main window of the application.
    ModifyPartController
    Handles all events within the ModifyPart window.
    ModifyProductController
    Handles all events within the ModifyProduct window.
    Outsourced
    Subclass of part which is sourced from another company.
    Part
    Abstract superclass which contains all the shared fields and methods of Outsourced & InHouse parts.
    Product
    Product which may have an associated parts list.
